edu.ncsu.csc216.travel.model.office

Interface TravelManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TourCoordinator

    public interface TravelManager
    TravelManager specifies the behaviors necessary to manage trips, clients, and reservations. Every class that implements TravelManager must have lists of clients and trips, each of which has its own list of reservations. The list of trips can be filtered.
    Author:
    Jo Perry

        Parameters:
        clientIndex - location of the client in the list of clients
        filteredTourIndex - location of the tour in the list of tours restricted to the current filters

        Throws:

        CapacityException - if the tour does not have the capacity to accommodate the reservation
